01:22:24.960 --> 01:22:30.210
And then some-- in terms of
culture, in other places,

01:22:30.210 --> 01:22:33.350
they might [inaudible] confusion
is that the best is sent

01:22:33.350 --> 01:22:36.450
in the world and the
