I forget who it is that says
they offered me the possibility

01:31:19.800 --> 01:31:23.630
of being an exile which
had all of consequences--

01:31:23.630 --> 01:31:24.930
&gt;&gt; Luis Roniger: Dorfman.

01:31:24.930 --> 01:31:26.230
&gt;&gt; Juan Uriagereka:
Dorfman, right?

01:31:26.230 --> 01:31:27.530
&gt;&gt; Saúl Sosnowski: Yeah.

