01:31:51.750 --> 01:31:54.930
on higher education,
in public policy,

01:31:54.930 --> 01:31:57.230
in governmental approaches
to [inaudible],

01:31:57.230 --> 01:32:00.550
redemocratization and so on.

01:32:00.550 --> 01:32:04.470
There is no question that we
